headline: SPPP- An ETF for Profiting from Two Promising Metals
summary: The market is weathering rising uncertainty so far, as every major group of companies in the index, from banks to commodities, has climbed since the low point in April. This brings me to the Sprott Physical Platinum and Palladium Trust (SPPP), writes Carl Delfeld, editor of Cabot Explorer.
